T1  - Tests of equal accuracy for nested models with estimated factors
AU  - Gonçalves, Sílvia
AU  - McCracken, Michael W.
AU  - Perron, Benoit
JO  - Journal of Econometrics
VL  - 198
IS  - 2
SP  - 231
